(50, 'Some By Mi Miracle Serum', 1500, 0, 'Benefits:\r\n\r\nHighly concentrated tea tree serum that changes the condition of your skin in just 30 days!\r\n\r\nActively soothes and calms irritated, damaged skin.\r\n\r\nDiminishes the appearance of blemishes.\r\n\r\nRemoves stubborn dead skin cells.\r\n\r\nShrinks pore size for a smooth complexion.\r\n\r\nAHA sloughs off dead cells and impurities on the skin\'s surface. BHA removes impurities and sebum inside pores. PHA prevents moisture loss.\r\n\r\nDermatologically tested.', 0, 'https://www.yesstyle.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/miracle_5.jpg', 4),
(51, 'Some By Mi Yuja Niacin Serum', 1500, 0, 'A serum containing Yuzu extract and niacinamide to diminish the appearance of blemishes in 30 days.\r\nA dual functional product: Whitening + Anti-wrinkle.\r\nContains 82% of Korean Yuja Extract for brightening and moisturising.\r\nWith 5% of Niacinamide to brighten up skin.\r\nPrevents the forming of melanin with Glutathione and Arbutin.\r\nRevitalises dull skin and ease off skin stress with 12 types of Vitamins.\r\nIt lightweight texture let skin absorb easily and leaves skin without sticky feeling.', 0, 'https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/31kSVFLsc5L.jpg', 4),
(52, 'Some By Mi Snail True Serum', 1500, 0, 'Multifunctional serum brightens skin while also combating signs of aging! Its formula is enriched with snail mucin to help regenerate skin cells while Truecica soothes skin and refines its texture.\r\n\r\nBenefits:\r\n\r\nA dual functional product: Whitening + Anti-wrinkle. Contains 890,000ppm of Snail Truecica™ which consists of Black Snail Extract and Truecica™. Helps for skin regeneration to repair skin damage with Black Snail Extract. Soothes skin and reinforces skin barrier with Truecica™. Removes blemishes and scar with a non-sticky finish. Free of 20 harmful ingredients. Passes skin irritation test.', 0, 'https://file.hstatic.net/1000006063/file/207_7ff5549a75514b51834744fe9991e063_master.jpg', 4),
(53, 'Kojic Serum', 650, 0, 'Kojic Serum is a powerful skincare product that will penetrate the deepest layers of your skin, leaving the skin feeling plump, radiant, glowing. It helps to remove black spots on the skin. This Kojic serum will make the skin smooth and Nourishing. Kojic serum will keep your skin tighter. the ingredients of kojic serum Protect the skin from damaging the sun UV. the Depth of this serum will protect the moisture.', 0, 'https://beautyliven.com/506-thickbox_default/kojic-serum-intensive-skin-whitening-and-brightening-power.jpg', 3),
(54, 'Cathy Doll Sunscream (ml-138)', 1000, 0, 'Skin Whitening\r\nWaterproof\r\nSkin Moisturizing\r\nSun Protection\r\nPore Tightening\r\nAll-in-one moisturizing hydration, sunscreen protection and heat-warding product especially for you.', 0, 'https://cdn.beautyboothqa.com/media/7NhjhNSNNwVMSwSgA3iHDfgEVa9v01TtisY14IWY.jpeg', 3),
(55, 'Cathy Doll Sunscream (ml-60)', 650, 0, 'Skin Whitening\r\nWaterproof\r\nSkin Moisturizing\r\nSun Protection\r\nPore Tightening\r\nAll-in-one moisturizing hydration, sunscreen protection and heat-warding product especially for you.', 0, 'https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media.evaly.com.bd/media/images/8acc85b71d38-60ml.png', 4),
(56, 'Snail Gluta Serum', 850, 0, 'Benefits:\nWhitens and smoothens face\nReduces appearance of fine lines\nEliminates dark spots\nTightens pores\nAnti-Aging properties:\nSuper active concentrated serum that deeply absorbs by your skin whitening skin and moisturizes skin at the same time with snail mucus extracts that is known to keep your skin healthy and glowing', 0, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0267/4963/2615/products/Screenshot_437_grande.png?', 6),
(57, 'The Elf Nano-White Gel', 1200, 0, 'PRODUCT DETAIL\r\n  Nano White Gel, the best skin nourishing gel , and supreme whitening.\r\n  Concentrated gel to help IMPROVE dark skin and accumulated dry skin.To be bright, clear, smooth, healthy\r\n  With premium extracts Imported from Switzerland Nano-small molecules Nourishing the skin deeply\r\n  Supuer anti-oxidant to keep skin youthful\r\n  Inhibit melanin that cause of darken and dull skin.\r\n  Restore Refresh skin ,keep moisturizing all day\r\n  Anti aging and \r\n  Reduce dark spot  , \r\n  Improve skin tone \r\n  Skin smooth and soft\r\n  \r\nINGREDIENT\r\n  NANO WHITE \r\n  RED ALGAE\r\n  JAPAN CUCUMBER\r\n  ALOE VERA\r\n  STRAWBERRY EXTRACT\r\n  RASPBERRY EXTRACT\r\n  TOMATO\r\n  CHERRY\r\n  VITAMIN B3.', 0, 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/hHwAAOSwqzFdvS12/s-l400.jpg', 6),
(58, 'Cathy Doll White Milk Shine Lotion', 1200, 0, 'White Milk Shine Body Lotion provides intensive fresh milk-like texture that instantly penetrates into the skin. Nourish skin deeply into the cellular level with the property from Milk Protein and White Strawberry that are rich in minerals and various vitamins. It helps to brighten the skin like a white strawberry texture that can lighten the color by itself until it turns into a white color appearance with the natural mechanism. Moreover, it helps neutralize dry skin to become smooth to the touch while bringing out a naturally bright appearance at the same time.', 0, 'https://beautyliven.com/148-thickbox_default/cathy-doll-white-milk-shine-lotion.jpg', 6);
