(59, 'Baby Bright Glutathione & Vit C Lotion', 750, 0, 'Caviar extract, this lotion helps protect your complexion from wrinkles and blemishes.\r\nFurthermore, Ginseng mix is well-suited to stimulate peeling. Coupled\r\nwith the sweet fragrance from flowers, your mind will be refreshed for the day.', 0, 'https://www.maruaygroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/BABY-BRIGHT-GLUTATHIONE-VIT-C-LOTION.....png', 6),
