(62, 'Marica Aura Body Toner', 650, 0, 'Help to remove black stains, black spot.. This contains Manuka Honey which helps to remove the stain on your skin, nourishing the skin before showering like having a skin spa. To soften, moisture and brighten the skin.', 0, 'https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/media.evaly.com.bd/media/images/47de569bfbda-marika-body-aura-toner.jpg', 6),
(63, 'Rose Smoothie Body Scrub', 1500, 10, 'Roses will leave your skin soft smooth and supple as they have a natural astringent effect on skin. Rose petals will tighten skin and shrink large pores, keeping skin fresh and toned.', 0, 'https://scontent.fdac5-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70745130_1128928813977825_2187929694328848384_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&_nc_sid=8bfeb9&_nc_eui2=AeEn3n56mMamA8PQyWToOzjeEaWVVI-0SmcRpZVUj7RKZ61nk2P7gHirVGzD3lMA1xK7ugWq3m4J14hKFuKDG1CA&_nc_ohc=e_mRj_KWiR4AX_kMm5f&_nc_ht=scontent.fdac5-1.fna&oh=e726eaf59312571b65a532ddd43944e1&oe=5F764516', 6),
(64, 'Baby Bright Glutathione & Vit C Shower Lotion', 1200, 0, 'Have a pleasant bath experience with 2-in-1 shower lotion.\r\n\r\nGlutathione and Vitamin C content is believed to brighten your skin that fully absorbs and nourishes the skin.\r\n\r\nThis special formula contains features that make your skin brighter 8-levels.\r\n\r\nThe 2 in 1 function as a Shower (soap bath) and lotion (moisturizer) that blends produce bright skin.\r\n\r\nYou no longer need to use any lotion after bathing.', 0, 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/zw4WUG8hnQwsEzOTyMlYnW2NGWBWFtlk3MiQq3tydatDioK3xTqOWJqZa3dCpZU8E6Vv12kmujhbDhK3JbM0ggrNtpI_XsoByoJRXz0qKkBBH3iJRh5jR-_yOTCoUgWWIF8T8oG51jA', 6),
