(70, 'Namu Life Snail White Body Booster S.P.F cc', 2000, 0, 'An ultra-lightweight and oil-free CC cream to protect skin against harmful rays.\r\n•	Boosts skin\r\n•	Protects against UVA/UVB rays, pollution and free radical damage\r\n•	Conceals dark spots and redness for flawless coverage\r\n•	Sweeps away dull surface cells for instantly glowing skin\r\n•	Packed with the intensive nourishment of snail secretion filtrate and Alps Edelweisse flower extract\r\n•	Provides natural radiance for a photo-ready look', 0, 'https://cf.shopee.ph/file/514e52d8dd82c0dd50d97ce47233663f_tn', 5),
