(79, 'Colla Zinc Plus C', 1000, 0, 'COLLA Zinc Plus C is the genuine collagen imported from Japan. It contains no powder and sugar, so you get the benefits of pure collagen effectively. It is easy to drink, not fishy, and helps replace collagen in bones, skin, tendons, muscles, and vascular wall for strong nails, hair, and bones, and youthful-looking skin.\n', 0, 'https://beautyliven.com/1080-large_default/colla-zinc-plus-c.jpg', 7),
